  "intent_precise": "3. Illumina DNA Prep - Amplify Tagmented DNA: Using mag_plate (pcr_plate, slot PCR plate), reagent_plate (plate, slot reagent plate), index plate (pcr_plate, slot 1), waste (reservoir, slot 5). With temperature module, magnetic module. (1) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (2) Disengage magnets to release beads. (3) Pause: \n\n\n\nReplace 200ul filtertipracks before resuming.\n\n\n\n (4) Transfer from source to liquid_trash A1. (5) Transfer from source to destination. (6) Engage magnets for bead separation. (7) Incubate for 3 minutes. (8) Disengage magnets to release beads. (9) Transfer from source to destination. (10) Mix vol_mix times. (11) Wait 2 seconds. (12) Pause: Seal the sample plate and centrifuge at 280 \u00d7 g for 3 seconds (13) Transfer from source to destination. (14) Mix reps_mix times at 20\u00b5L. (15) Wait 2 seconds.",
